===下落不明界碑===
另外，在[[馬己仙峽道|馬己仙峽道]]15號亦證實本來存有一塊界碑，但該界碑於2007年6月被人移走，引起部份社會人士關注<ref>{{Cite web|title=Boundary Stone at Magazine Gap Road|url=https://gwulo.com/boundary-stone-at-magazine-gap-road|accessdate=2020-02-03|author=|date=2007|format=|publisher=Gwulo: Old Hong Kong|language=en|archive-date=2020-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203055533/https://gwulo.com/boundary-stone-at-magazine-gap-road|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://blog.yahoo.com/Daniel-C/articles/13318 重新消失了的界碑石]</ref><ref>{{cite news|author = |url = http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20070817/10037668|title = 探針：界石失蹤政府不聞不問|work = 蘋果日報|page = |date = 2007-08-17|accessdate = 2012-10-29|archive-date = 2015-08-31|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150831013856/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20070817/10037668|dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author = |url = http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20070819/10044267|title = 百年古物網上掀拯救行動專題報道：第七界石神秘消失|work = 蘋果日報|page = A6 |date = 2007-08-19|accessdate = 2012-10-29|archive-date = 2016-01-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160125031151/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20070819/10044267|dead-url = no}}</ref>，至今下落仍不明。

